---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Laboratory Furnace Consumables For Research And Testing" description="You require high-precision components for research and testing repeatability. Our laboratory-grade furnace accessories provide industrial reliability for R&D.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Laboratory Furnace Consumables For Research And Testing</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You require high-precision components to ensure the repeatability and accuracy of your metallurgical research and material testing. Our laboratory-grade furnace accessories are designed to provide the same reliability as our industrial products but on a scale suited for R&D facilities. You will achieve more accurate data and more reliable experimental results by utilizing our specialized heating elements, thermocouples, and small-scale insulation solutions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Lab furnaces often struggle with temperature overshoot and uneven heating in small chambers. You need extreme precision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu provides specialized lab-scale heating elements and high-accuracy probes. You maintain 100% control over your testing environment, every time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Precision Lab Sensors</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Mini-Heating Elements</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Small Alumina Tubes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Fiber Insulation Boards</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Lab Furnace Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
